data.description: Wonderful one level home with a huge corner lot located in the Western Hills neighborhood . Close to shopping , restaurants and hospitals. Updates include HVAC(2021) , water heater (2021), updated bathrooms, interior and exterior paint , new deck in the spacious relaxing fully fenced backyard. Refrigerator , washer and dryer convey to make the move in easier for your buyer(s) ! Don't miss this opportunity to make this well maintained home your forever home!
